### Get it as a NuGet Package [here] (http://www.nuget.org/packages/VirtualObjects/)
```
   PM> Install-Package VirtualObjects -Pre
```

### Dependencies
* Castle.Core       (≥ 3.2.2)
* fasterflect       (≥ 2.1.3)
* Ninject           (≥ 3.0.1.10)
